---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="All Saints Anglican School Case Study - Wearthy" description="Discover how Wearthy transformed All Saints Anglican School's playground into a nature-inspired learning environment for grades 3-6 students.">
	<header class="header case-study-header" role="banner">
		<div class="hero-overlay"></div>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header-content">
				<div class="logo-container">
					<a href="/" class="logo-link">
						<img src="/wearthy-logo.png" alt="Wearthy" class="logo-image" />
					</a>
				</div>
				<h1 class="hero-title">All Saints Anglican School</h1>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">A Nature-Inspired Playground for Grades 3-6</p>
				<div class="project-meta">
					<span class="meta-item">Queensland</span>
					<span class="meta-separator">•</span>
					<span class="meta-item">Primary School (Grades 3-6)</span>
					<span class="meta-separator">•</span>
					<span class="meta-item">Nature Play Design</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<main class="case-study-main">

		<div class="container case-study-container">
			<section class="brief-section">
				<h2>The Brief</h2>
				<p class="large-text">
					The client approached us to design a play structure for older children (Years 3–6). The site already featured several mature trees, and the goal was to create a challenging, gross-motor-focused treehouse-style play space that made use of the existing natural elements.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="before-after-section">
				<h2>Before & After</h2>
				<div class="comparison-grid">
					<div class="comparison-item">
						<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/AllSaintsBefore.jpg" alt="All Saints playground before transformation" class="comparison-image" loading="lazy" />
						<p class="comparison-label">Before</p>
					</div>
					<div class="comparison-item">
						<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/AllSaintsCover.jpg" alt="All Saints playground after transformation" class="comparison-image" loading="lazy" />
						<p class="comparison-label">After</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="gallery-section">
				<h2>The Transformation</h2>
				<div class="photo-gallery">
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01103-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground feature" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01106-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground climbing structure" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01109-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground slide" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01113-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground balance elements" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01119-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground obstacle course" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01122-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground play space" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01125-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground natural elements" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01130-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground treehouse structure" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01133-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground climbing feature" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01136-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground detail" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01141-HDR.jpg" alt="All Saints playground challenge course" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/AllSaints/optimized/DSC01143-HDR-1.jpg" alt="All Saints playground overview" class="gallery-image" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="testimonial-section">
				<div class="testimonial-card">
					<div class="quote-icon">"</div>
					<blockquote>
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							The new playground has been a fantastic addition to our school! One of the standout features is the giant slide, which has quickly become a favorite among the children. Its size and speed bring a real sense of excitement and joy to playtime.
						</p>
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							Equally popular is the physical challenge aspect of the playground. The climbing structures, balance elements, and obstacle-style features encourage students to test their strength, coordination, and confidence in a fun and safe environment. It's wonderful to see so many children engaged, active, and smiling as they explore the space.
						</p>
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							Overall, the playground has not only enhanced outdoor play but also supports physical development and social interaction. A big win for our school community!
						</p>
					</blockquote>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<p class="author-name">All Saints Anglican School</p>
						<p class="author-title">Queensland</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="philosophy-section">
				<h2>The Ecology of Play</h2>
				<p class="large-text">
					Our design approach is grounded in the Ecology of Play framework, which recognizes that children need three essential elements for healthy development through play:
				</p>

				<div class="pillars-grid">
					<div class="pillar">
						<div class="pillar-icon">1</div>
						<h3>Unstructured Time</h3>
						<p>Spaces that allow children to simply be, without every moment managed or optimized. Children need time to explore, discover, and create their own play experiences.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="pillar">
						<div class="pillar-icon">2</div>
						<h3>Freedom to Choose</h3>
						<p>Environments that support independent decision-making, even if choices lead to failure. This autonomy builds confidence and resilience.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="pillar">
						<div class="pillar-icon">3</div>
						<h3>Endless Possibilities</h3>
						<p>Spaces that whisper "what if?" instead of dictating "you must." Rich environments that inspire imagination and support diverse play types.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p class="large-text" style="margin-top: 40px;">
					At All Saints Anglican School, we applied these principles to create a treehouse-style playground that integrates with mature trees, offering physical challenges and natural play experiences that support the developmental needs of Years 3-6 students.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="cta-section">
				<div class="cta-card">
					<h2>Ready to Transform Your School's Play Environment?</h2>
					<p>
						Book a free discovery call for your school. Expert designs, accurate costings,
						and grant application support.
					</p>
					<div class="cta-buttons">
						<a href="/forms/discovery-call" class="btn-primary">Book Discovery Call</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>

	<footer class="site-footer">
		<div class="container">
			<p>&copy; 2024 Wearthy. The playful beginnings of human flourishing.</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.case-study-header {
		background: url('/AllSaints/optimized/AllSaintsCover.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
		min-height: 500px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		position: relative;
		color: white;
		padding: 60px 0;
	}

	.hero-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 74, 58, 0.65), rgba(139, 119, 101, 0.55));
		backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.case-study-header .container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.logo-container {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}

	.logo-link {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 15px 35px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.logo-link:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	.logo-image {
		height: 100px;
		width: auto;
		display: block;
		filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
		drop-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}

	.header-content {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		line-height: 1.2;
		font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
		color: white;
		text-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
		line-height: 1.6;
		text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.project-meta {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 10px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}

	.meta-separator {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
	}

	.case-study-container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		padding: 80px 20px;
	}

	.brief-section,
	.before-after-section,
	.gallery-section,
	.testimonial-section,
	.philosophy-section,
	.cta-section {
		margin-bottom: 80px;
	}

	.brief-section h2,
	.before-after-section h2,
	.gallery-section h2,
	.philosophy-section h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #5a4a3a;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
	}

	.comparison-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 40px;
		margin-top: 40px;
	}

	.comparison-item {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.comparison-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(90, 74, 58, 0.15);
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}

	.comparison-label {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #5a4a3a;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
	}

	.photo-gallery {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 20px;
		margin-top: 40px;
	}

	.gallery-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: 250px;
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(90, 74, 58, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.gallery-image:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(90, 74, 58, 0.2);
	}

	.large-text {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #6b5b4b;
	}


	.testimonial-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 60px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(90, 74, 58, 0.08);
		position: relative;
	}

	.quote-icon {
		font-size: 6rem;
		color: #e8dcc6;
		line-height: 1;
		position: absolute;
		top: 20px;
		left: 40px;
		font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
	}

	.testimonial-text {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #5a4a3a;
		font-style: italic;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
	}

	.testimonial-author {
		text-align: right;
		padding-top: 20px;
		border-top: 2px solid #e8dcc6;
	}

	.author-name {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #5a4a3a;
		margin-bottom: 5px;
	}

	.author-title {
		color: #8b7765;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.pillars-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 40px;
		margin-top: 50px;
	}

	.pillar {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 30px;
	}

	.pillar-icon {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b8a690, #8b7765);
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: white;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin: 0 auto 20px;
	}

	.pillar h3 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		color: #5a4a3a;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.pillar p {
		color: #6b5b4b;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-card {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b8a690, #8b7765);
		color: white;
		padding: 60px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-card h2 {
		color: white;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.cta-card p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 35px;
		opacity: 0.95;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 20px;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b8a690 0%, #8b7765 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 16px 35px;
		border-radius: 6px;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		text-decoration: none;
		display: inline-block;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-1px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(139, 119, 101, 0.3);
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a69580 0%, #7a6654 100%);
	}

	.site-footer {
		background: #5a4a3a;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		padding: 40px 0;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.case-study-header {
			min-height: 400px;
			padding: 40px 0;
		}

		.logo-image {
			height: 80px;
		}

		.hero-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.hero-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		.comparison-grid,
		.photo-gallery,
		.pillars-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 30px;
		}

		.gallery-image {
			height: 200px;
		}

		.testimonial-card {
			padding: 40px 30px;
		}

		.quote-icon {
			font-size: 4rem;
			top: 10px;
			left: 20px;
		}

		.cta-card {
			padding: 40px 30px;
		}

		.cta-card h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: stretch;
		}
	}
</style>
